      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136798
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b166",
      "text": "from [/villagepump/小説は経験の共有手段]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b167",
      "text": "from [独自の用語を造語する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b168",
      "text": "小説は経験の共有手段",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b169",
      "text": "[経験によって獲得したものを説明することは困難]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16a",
      "text": "[深い説明は説明者にとってコスト]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16b",
      "text": "\t[小説]はこういう課題に立ち向かっている例のように思う[/villagepump/inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16c",
      "text": "\t\t主人公に[感情移入]させたりする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16d",
      "text": "\t[小説は経験の共有手段]ということかー[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16e",
      "text": "　　確かに「ザ・ゴール」みたいな、小説形式で経験を共有して抽象的な概念をわかりやすく伝えるメソッドはあるな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
    {
      "id": "63f7139baff09e000089b16f",
      "text": "　　数学ガールもそう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677136796,
      "updated": 1677136796
    },
